      <abstract>
        <p>A J Wright, part of TJX Companies, to Link Agency to handle account of discount retailer, which had been at Holland Mark Edmund Ingalls; billings estimated at $4 million (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>* A. J. Wright, Framingham, Mass., part of the TJX Companies, to the Link Agency, Providence, R.I., to handle the account of the discount retailer, which had been at Holland Mark Edmund Ingalls, Boston. Billings were estimated at $4 million.</p>
